              {
                "description": "<p> The value assigned to this exported environment variable. </p> <note> <p> During a build, the value of a variable is available starting with the <code>install</code> phase. It can be updated between the start of the <code>install</code> phase and the end of the <code>post_build</code> phase. After the <code>post_build</code> phase ends, the value of exported variables cannot change.</p> </note>"
